release_note: Thanks for updating Habio! Welcome to the new and improved Habio! In this release we ve crushed a bunch of pesky bugs boosted performance and added some new content to keep you motivated on your journey to success. Thank you for being part of the Habio community and inspiring us to keep striving for excellence. We re always here for you so please don t hesitate to reach out with any feedback or questions. And keep an eye out for future updates as we ve got big plans in store.

Thanks for updating Habio! We re happy and excited to bring you Habio 4.0! In this release we ve fixed a few bugs improved stability and added fresh content so there s much to explore. Plus our team has been working on some great new features we can t wait to share with you. Thanks for supporting us and coming along for the ride! If you run into any issues with this update please don t hesitate to let us know.
